Package bolt.web.coffee.io

Interface Summary
CoffeeGraphOptions Implementation prototype for the output options generated by Coffee-Graph.
CoffeeGraphOptionsParser An implementation prototype for an object which creates CoffeeGraphOptions implementations.
Exporter Implementation prototype for an object which accepts dependency information and exports it based on specified options.
ExporterFactory The implementation prototype for an object that generates Exporter instances.
Lexer Implementation prototype for a coffee-script tokenizer.
Parser Implementation prototype for a coffee-script parser.
 

Class Summary
CoffeeScriptLexer This class uses a CoffeeScript instance, which uses rhino to execute the javascript coffee-script utilities.
CoffeeScriptMinParser This class creates a CoffeeTree using the tokens generated by the CoffeeScriptLexer.
CoffeeToken This class represents a lexical token in the Coffee Script language.
DefaultExporterFactory The default ExporterFactory implementation, which chains Coffee-Graph usage options together.
